Interface FloatIndexedContainer

@Generated(date="2021-12-15T09:45:36+0100", value="KTypeIndexedContainer.java") public interface FloatIndexedContainer extends FloatCollection, RandomAccess
An indexed container provides random access to elements based on an index. Indexes are zero-based.
